can have multiple attribute values.
values always be in " " double quote.
we can have an attribute with out value too.

for name and id attributes always one value
for class attribute can have multiple values and separated by space

id one value always unique if we found two html code with same it is a bug should be reported
name one value 99% unique
class multiple values and usually duplicate

if we have id in a code should always go with id then name then class

linkedtext : not an attributes related to the text used with anker tag or a tag
partiallinkedtext : not an attributes related to the text

